title: Andy Gibb - The Best Of Andy Gibb
description:
Andy Gibb - The Best Of Andy Gibb (2001)

"20th Century Masters - The Millennium Collection"

These songs were released from 1977 to 1980.



01   I Just Want To Be Your Everything
02   Love Is Thicker Than Water
03   Shadow Dancing
04   An Everlasting Love
05   (Our Love) Don't Throw It All Away
06   After Dark
07   Desire
08   I Can't Help It      (duet with Olivia Newton-John)
09   Time Is Time
10   Me (Without You)
11   Will You Love Me Tomorrow    (duet with Pat Arnold)


--------------------------------------------------------

By the way, if you like the Bee Gees as well, 
I suggest the torrent of "Bee Gees - Best Of Volume 1 & 2 & Greatest"
